<description>Paint a Genome Scan picture from a BAM.</description>



<documentation>
<h:h3>Motivation</h:h3>

Plot the coverage of one or more BAMs. Save a picture as JPG.

Duplicates are removed.

<h:h3>Example</h:h3>

<h:pre class="bash"><!-- $  java -jar dist/bamgenscan.jar  --> --max-y 20 --image-size 2000x800 <!-- -o out.jpg f1.bam f2.bam f3.bam
 --></h:pre>
the figure displays the mean, min, max, median of the coverage. 

<h:img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Bfnu__LCAAEcJu4.jpg:large"/>

</documentation>


